include ../mixins/container

- var values = { title: 'Face a Setback', name: 'FaceASetback', class: 'face-a-setback', page: 'page X', radio: 'face_a_setback', stat: ``, stat_repeat: '' }
+container(values)
  p When your momentum is at its minimum (-6), make a moveyou’re your action die matches your negative momentum, you must cancel your action die.
  p If you suffer additional -momentum, choose one.
  ul
    li Exchange each additional -momentum for any combination of -health, -spirit, -supply, -wealth or -companion’s loyalty as appropriate to the circumstances.
    li Envision an event or discovery which undermines your progress in a current quest, journey or fight. Then, for each additional -momentum, clear 1 unit of progress on that track per its rank (troublesome=clear 3 progress; dangerous=clear 2 progress; formidable=clear 1 progress; extreme=clear 2 ticks; epic=clear 1 tick).